      "rationale": "At the chosen settings (h_base = 0.35 mm, C_mu = 0.09, gamma_th = 500 s⁻¹), mean absolute error in RH index is 4.2% and maximum error is 8.7% across five operating points. Systematic bias is 2.1%. Acceptance criteria met. Results are conditional on the analyst-selected parameter values used during validation."
