    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per MRL 2 scoping guidance. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 at all five operating points confirms compliance with the acceptance criterion. The assessment is accepted subject to the configuration parameters used during validation (h_base, C_mu, gamma_th) being applied consistently in deployment runs; however, no machine-readable configuration binding enforces this requirement.",
